/anei̯siwiwiɾi/: [mi nɑ̟ ɑ̟fu se̝nsi nɔ̝ wɑ̟n mɑ̟n e̝ bɾɔ̝kɔ̝ mi]
[ʊ̞bia̠ a̠ nʊ̞ fu ju nʊ̞ spiti na̠ ini]
[ju kɑ̟n t͡ʃibɾi ju ɡɾɑ̟mmːɑ̟ mɑ̟ ju nɔ̝ kɑ̟n t͡ʃibɾi e̝n kɔ̝sɔ̝kɔ̝sɔ̝]
/ju kan kibɾi ju ɡɾanmːa ma ju no kan kibɾi en kosokoso/
[mi na̠ a̠fu sɪ̞nsi nʊ̞ wa̠n ma̠n ɪ̞ bɾʊ̞kʊ̞ mi]
/mi na afu sensi no wan man e bɾoko mi/
[ju ka̠n cibɾi ju ɡɾa̠mmːa̠ ma̠ ju nʊ̞ ka̠n cibɾi ɪ̞n kʊ̞sʊ̞kʊ̞sʊ̞]
[ɔ̝biɑ̟ ɑ̟ nɔ̝ fu ju nɔ̝ spiti nɑ̟ ini]
/obia a no fu ju no spiti na ini/
